I remember a friend buying some sort of external foam sprayer system when he bought a house in an area with frequent wildfires. He ended up going with some sort of permanently installed external sprinkler thing, plus adding metal shutters that could be closed and designing the yard like a fire break.I don't think this is what he got, but the fact that this site exists amazes me: http://www.fdnntv.com/Foam-Safe-System
