Posted: Tue Jun 26, 2012 8:19 pm
Jesus Christ, Wingfooted posted while I was typing.The smoke column is flashing. WOW. That looks like the shit we had here (southern BC) in 2003. Fires one ridge over from where I was were in a park, so they let them burn. It rained on and off in Calgary for a week as all the water vapor from combustion nucleated out on the smoke.Keep your ass safe, yeah?
